targets.formattedQuery: SELECT $timeSeries as t, count() FROM $table WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY t ORDER BY t
targets.query:
SELECT count(*) AS GitHub FROM default.github
WHERE $timeFilterByColumn(TimeStamp) AND  EventType = 'push'
targets.rawQuery:
SELECT count(*) AS GitHub FROM default.github
WHERE TimeStamp >= toDateTime(1694224447) AND TimeStamp <= toDateTime(1694246047) AND  EventType = 'push'

panels.description: The panel displays the count of Push events on Azure by each author. It provides insights into the contribution activity of different authors within the specified repository.

targets.query:
SELECT Author, count(*) AS Azure_Push_Events
FROM default.azure_devops
WHERE $timeFilterByColumn(TimeStamp) AND EventType = 'git.push'
GROUP BY Author

FROM default.azure_devops
WHERE TimeStamp >= toDateTime(1694224224) AND TimeStamp <= toDateTime(1694245824) AND EventType = 'git.push'
GROUP BY Author
